(42230, 130054, 0, 1, '請留下妳的電話給我, 拜託！ Let me have your number, please！', '', '2012-01-13 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 4, '請留下妳的電話給我,拜託  Let me have your number, please!\r\n\r\n一場大雨下過的燥熱午後 我坐在車水馬路虎口 \r\nIn a hot afternoon after a pouring rain, I was sitting by a busy road.\r\n\r\n看著驚嚇的妳和嚇傻的我 我不知道該怎麼說\r\nYou and I were in shock, and I didn''t know what to say. \r\n\r\n汽機車逼逼巴巴催促著我 好心路人問我好不好過 \r\nCars and scooters were honking and someone asked me if I was alright. \r\n\r\n突然腦袋一片白光面閃過　下站天堂還是地獄等我　 \r\nA white light flashed by. “Is this heaven or hell?” \r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要陪我 我正享受著片刻心動 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need company. I was soaking up the moment. \r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要賠我 再多金錢也沒有用 醫不好我 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need compensation. All the money in the world was not going to cure me.\r\n\r\n一場大雨下過的燥熱午後 我的白日夢正上頭\r\nAfter a pouring rain in a hot afternoon, I was daydreaming. \r\n\r\n公主馬車變成賓士撞上我 哎唷 該怎麼說\r\nThe princess carriage turned into a Mercedes and hit me. “Damn! What the hell happened?”     \r\n\r\n汽機車逼逼巴巴催促著我　地上一堆紅白血球亂流\r\nCars and scooters were honking, and there was blood on the ground. \r\n\r\n但此刻我怎麼也會不痛　　希望妳會治好我的傷口 \r\nBut in that moment I didn''t feel pain, I was hoping you could heal my wounds.  \r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要陪我 我正享受著片刻心動 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need company. I was soaking up the moment. \r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要賠我 就算再多金錢也沒用 醫不好我 \r\nI did''t need medical attention, nor did I need compensation. All the money in the world was not going to cure me.\r\n\r\n視線模糊 心跳加速 就差一點 小明不見\r\nSight blurring, heart pumping, I was that close to being killed.\r\n\r\n此刻的妳 快步向前 拍拍了我的肩　說了很多抱歉　希望我別走再待一會兒\r\nAt that moment, you ran up to me, tapped my shoulder, and said a bunch of sorries; hoping I can hang in there.\r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要陪我 我正享受著片刻心動 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need company. I was soaking up the moment. \r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要賠我 再多金錢也沒有用 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need compensation. All the money in the world was not going to cure me.\r\n\r\n\r\n不需要急救 不需要陪我 請留下妳的電話給我 妳幹嘛玩我 \r\nI didn''t need medical attention, nor did I need company. Just let me have your number.\r\nWHY DID YOU LEAVE A FAKE NUMBER???', '', 200, '', '', '', '', '', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-13 12:26:00', '2015-03-12 13:50:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
