(42290, 125184, 4298, 1, '黑色相片', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\n\r\nBlack photo sings about how most photos will depict happier moments and fonder times but never displaying moments of loneliness and agony.In all manners of upsetting situations, will a photo be able to best describe your very disturbing mood. Time is captured and stalled but time will always heal.\r\nThis is TKB''s first single and made it across Singapore''s maintstream major radio stations YES 933fm, Love 103FM!\r\nIt is with this song that kept the station''s DJ inviting TKB for an exclusive interview and kept audiences humming to the chorus of this track.\r\nTKB wishes to travel across to Kenting to pull off all their best playability and bring good Singapore music to Taiwan!!!!!!!Rock and Roll~!!\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 7, '', '', 255, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:12:30', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
