(42292, 125184, 4298, 2, 'By Your Side', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\n\r\nBy Your Side is how the band stuck to one another during critical moments during our formation.From day one of jamming rehearsals to recording period.It is in  such harsh condition that brought us tigher under as one rocking band and a family of rocking attitude.TKB performs this track in every gig as an encore or last closing track for a set.\r\nThis track will get all on their feets and jump along to the thumping rhythm\r\nVocals by Kenny who also plays the bass.\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 1, '', '', 259, '', 'Kenny Ong', 'Kenny Ong', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:15:33', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42293, 125184, 4298, 4, '17号', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\nThis number is significant to TKB.This number is the unit number that houses TKB''s first private music rehearsal studio in Singapore.Fully-equipped for music writing,composing arrangements and a place whereby TKB comes in weekly to sing play and chat..This song writes about a love for an inanimate object.\r\nThis is TKB''s love at sight.no.17 will kick off with a dramatic music intro,which TKB often uses in their first song during live performances.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 40, 0, 1, '', '', 379, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:21:40', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42294, 125184, 4298, 5, '我好想', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\n\r\nA ballad is a must in every rock outfit.\r\nWith piano and soft chimes to add to a full blown flavour of  a rock band going soft with this track to signify TKB''s versatility.\r\nThis song sings about the loss of loved ones to an unrequited love.Love ilfe''s ups and downs is well-represented in the song progressing structure with key changes and harmonising guitar solos.\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 40, 0, 1, '', '', 269, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Shan Ng', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:24:28', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42295, 125184, 4298, 6, '忠于自己', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\n\r\nBeing loyal to our individualistic identity as a person.Accepting as who we are,as a band, as a person,TKB represents an attitude not only in our character but deeply represented in our music,in this track.\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 40, 0, 1, '', '', 208, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Putt CR', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:30:32', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42296, 125184, 4298, 3, '我们是TKB', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\nThis song writes about the Band''s self -titled track "we areTKB" further introducing ourselves and reinforcing our positive attitude in reviving Singapore''s homegrown music scene.Start with TKB.Be ready to headbang and bounce to this heavy hearted and dynamic grooves to this TKB''s music!Featuring Kenny Ong rapping !\r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 1, '', '', 275, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan & TKB', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:32:59', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
(42297, 125184, 4298, 7, '第一步。第一部', 'TKB''s first move into maintstream music debutting with this "First step" titled 7-track EP.\r\nWritten acoustically including a violin arrangement for an earful of melancholy rock with a dynamic vocal-Nicole to add to the melodic acoustic track.Derricks performs and records all the instruments from bass to drums to guitars.\r\nAll violin arrangements courtesy of Joan Chew \r\n\r\nTKB\r\n \r\n', '2011-07-01 00:00:00', 2011, 0, 1, 1, '', '', 253, '', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan', 'Derrick Chan', 'TKB Productions', '', 1, 1, 0, '2012-01-15 12:35:29', '2015-03-12 13:50:01', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
